  weather  — get current weather for a city via wttr.in JSON API                            detail
────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

    runtime       http
    method        GET
    url           https://wttr.in/{{city}}?format=j1
    max resp      10.0 MB
    private net   blocked
    timeout       60s

    args
    
    city  string · required

    usage
    
